description: "Produced by the British Admiralty’s Hydrographic Office, this map includes various navigational aids, such as maritime routes, bathymetry (sea depth), tide and current data, and elevations (side views of hills and mountains to use as landmarks)."
title: "Gulf of Siam. Malay Peninsula - East Coast. Lakon Roads to Lem Tane / surveyed by commander A.J. Loftus and officers of the Siamese Navy 1872 ; engraved by Davies & Company."
